        "created_at": "2004-12-30T23:01:23.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>every single animation that is used in the game is in anim.hqr, it may just be a case of searching for it. you can use a cntrl+f search on <a href=\"http://chaosfish.free.fr/lbafileinfo/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">this</a> page, 216 is zoe walking (lba1), and there are a nice set of lba1 animations for fighting etc cause of the zoe clones. if you wanted to make a set for, say a grobo, you will find it harder because there is no animation for a grobo throwing a magic ball. inter-race body swaps are hard, but possible. anyway, there you go. welcome to the forums:D</p>",
